description:
User logs in their account. And navigates to account overview
    to view their account details.

elements.name: User is able to see their account details.

steps.name: The user lands at the webpage.
User registers new user account.
The user is logged in successfully.
The user navigates to account overview tab.
User is able to see account number, balance, available amount and total balance.

name: User is able to view their account details.
